name: Computer Test of Nopcommerce
description: As a user I should verify the computer and desktops functionality

children.name: verify user should navigate to computer page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer tab
And I should verify the computer text "Computers"
verify user should navigate to desktops page successfully
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer tab
And I click on desktops tab
And I should verify the desktops text "Desktops"
verify that user should build and add your own computer into cart

children.name: verify that user should build and add your own computer into cart
Given I am on homepage
When I click on computer tab
And I click on desktops tab
And I click on build your own computer
And I select processor "2.2 GHz Intel Pentium Dual-Core E2200"
And I select ram "2 GB"
And I select Hdd radio "320 GB"
And I select OS radio "Vista Home [+$50.00]"
And I select software "Acrobat Reader [+$10.00]"
And I click on add to cart button
Then I should verify the add to cart message"The product has been added to your shopping cart"
verify that user should build and add your own computer into cart

And I select Hdd radio "400 GB [+$100.00]"

And I select software "Acrobat Reader [+$10.00]"

verify that user should build and add your own computer into cart

When I click on computer tab

And I click on login button
Then I should not logged in with invalid credentials
